name: Evil Tree
description:
Girls burnout shirt with pen and ink drawing of a tree with fangs. The graphic is printed in dark purple, almost black.

3.1 oz., 50% ringspun cotton, 50% polyester. Fabric made through an extensive process that shows years of weathering; each bit of pilling and striation in this sheer fabric captures the true old vintage worn-in feel. 1 x 1 burnout rib collar. Shoulder-to-shoulder neck tape. Blind stitching on bottom hem and sleeves. Garment dyed pigment; enzyme/silicone finish. Side seamed. Set in sleeves. Each burnout garment will vary in shade and surface texture due to the intense weathering process used to achieve this one-of-a-kind look.
